title: Nordo In For PA! Krawczynski/Hayes/Greenway/Korzo/Grimm
description: Nordo is back in the big chair! The Athletic's Jon Krawczynski and Dan Hayes both spend some time on the phone, Chad Greenway is in studio to talk about the latest NFL news, Korzo is also in studio as is Mike Grimm!
